column5: Limited ice means, crowds. My go to spot seems to be over run the past few weeks. DAMIT.  Anyhoo,  Making the best of what we have been given by mother nature. My white fish mojo from last year ,seems to have left me. Working on getting it back.
slip slidin away.... that was a nice one.
Thanks and good to see the escapee sent a buddy back to replace them.
its all fun and games till someone loses a fish   lol oh wait it was fun after too

You could post whitey videos, say nothing of what you're fishing and by watching the rod tip still know that you're whitey fishing. Just the way they pull.  Good you're finally on the board. Now get back and get more while you still can.
